{"tid":606314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯爺孫戀,美女想懷下爺爺的孩子","createTime":"2018-03-26T11:21:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T15:09:52.000Z","uid":25345,"like":385,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"e16c441b8be605c3fc15f6c4adcb16cbbe36b983","tid":606314,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T11:21:17.000Z","msg":"現齡86歲的卡拉斯科在2010年認識當時年僅19歲娜塔莉，當時他在嫩妻就讀的大學教課，他的紳士風度、燦爛笑容、高智慧的氣質迷倒娜塔莉。在娜塔莉窮追猛打的寫情詩倒追後，他封陳已久的心也跟著打開，便與娜塔莉交往。卡拉斯科與娜塔莉談戀愛後，感情越來愈好，兩人之間幾乎沒有代溝，決定走上紅毯照顧彼此。<br />\n<br />\n卡拉斯科2015年在聖彼得堡舉行浪漫婚禮，他還特地穿上23歲時在前蘇聯海軍服役的軍服，他緊握嬌妻娜塔莉走上紅毯，在少數親朋好友的面前見證他們的愛情。卡拉斯科表示，已經好久沒有享受過這種年輕的感覺，「穿上軍服後就像23歲的小夥子，為了年紀小的妻子，我會努力活久一點來陪她。」<br />\n<br />\n卡拉斯科畢竟年歲已高，「性能力」是否滿足嫩妻也成為話題。娜塔莉表示，卡拉斯科平常會親吻她，也會擁抱她，這代表她們之間有過親密的接觸，「會盡量滿足她！」娜塔莉則表示，與「我是希望婚後能有小孩。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2870/d2870769.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2870%2Fd2870769.jpg&h=3b7d6cee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2870/d2870765.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2870%2Fd2870765.jpg&h=6cd279a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2870/d2870770.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2870%2Fd2870770.jpg&h=33496386&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://motherhoodinstyle.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/russian.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmotherhoodinstyle.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F09%2Frussian.jpg&h=e037450b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://infohow.net/7_kkr.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Finfohow.net%2F7_kkr.JPG&h=bdd00ed7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2870/d2870768.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2870%2Fd2870768.jpg&h=f7d76c70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b9283f36338641fb3350790aeb377db8ff19177","tid":606314,"uid":132039,"like":260,"dislike":8,"score":252,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T11:22:33.000Z","msg":"$$$<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"371098972350674cc60ca6204af8a63e1fc32370","tid":606314,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T11:22:50.000Z","msg":"龜市爺爺"},{"pid":"a2257e8f8b61f2f2f2dbcae43d5cded81386a30d","tid":606314,"uid":25345,"like":249,"dislike":5,"score":244,"quote":{"pid":"371098972350674cc60ca6204af8a63e1fc32370","tid":606314,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T11:22:50.000Z","msg":"龜市爺爺"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T11:24:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5898102-77f4ab6ca85319c5?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/369\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload-images.jianshu.io%2Fupload_images%2F5898102-77f4ab6ca85319c5%3FimageMogr2%2Fauto-orient%2Fstrip%257CimageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F369&h=69a09602&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a0d97866f6b87aaae8da513eb6855e25c2fbcc9","tid":606314,"uid":20867,"like":118,"dislike":4,"score":114,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T11:24:53.000Z","msg":"「狗屎，這怎麼可能？」"},{"pid":"4220570bf54fd9c8552ed3635292065d6e35d550","tid":606314,"uid":31215,"like":69,"dislike":1,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T11:26:30.000Z","msg":"非洲打獵故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd27905925df8d4611fd17d0a8589d128bb08ac","tid":606314,"uid":85557,"like":82,"dislike":1,"score":81,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T11:27:46.000Z","msg":"好快有身家分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> fat fat啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c2bac1a2d8c551828b30f32e5e82c62ab456ded","tid":606314,"uid"